condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :LA Article V, 5.01 (a) | Description :Effectiveness Conditions: the Subsidiary Agreement has been executed onbehalf of the Republic of Azerbaijan and SFDI. | Due Date :31-Mar-2012
Finance Agreement :LA Article V, 5.01 (b) | Description :Effectiveness Conditions: SFDI has adopted the revised Operational Manual,satisfactory to the Bank. | Due Date :01-Jan-2012

Finance Agreement :LA Schedule 2, Section I, A; PA Schedule, Section 1, A | Description :Implementation Conditions: The Republic ofAzerbaijan shall cause SFDI to carry out the Project in accordance with Loan Agreement, the Project Agreement, SubsidiaryAgreement, the Operations Manual. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :LA Schedule 2, Section I, D1; PA Schedule, Section I, C1 | Description :Safeguard Conditions: The Republic ofAzerbaijan shall ensure that the Project is carried out by SFDI in accordance with the provisions of the EMPF. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :LA Schedule 2, Section I, D2; PA Schedule, Section I, C2 | Description :Safeguard Conditions: SFDI shall ensurethat works are implemented in accordance with site specific EMP. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :LA Schedule 2, Section II, A1; PA Schedule, Section II, A. | Description :Reporting Conditions: SFDI shallsubmit progress reports based on agreed upon indicators to the Bank each quarter. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :LA Schedule 2, Section IV, B1 | Description :Retroactive Financing: no withdrawal for payments made prior to thedate of the LA, apart from withdrawals not to exceed an amount $800,000 on or after October 15, 2011 for eligible expenses. | DueDate :01-Jan-2010
